message.content:
The environment contains a kitchen and dining area. 
In the kitchen area, there are black cabinets with marble countertops and a sink. On the countertop, there are various items including a pot, a jar of jam, a puzzle box, a Rice Bubbles box, a Jello box, a plate, and a cup. 
Above the countertop, there is a wooden-framed mirror and a vent hood. 
To the right of the kitchen area, there is a white refrigerator against the wall. 
In the dining area, there is a wooden table with four white chairs. On the table, there are two bottles of water. 
The floor is made of dark wood parquet, and the walls are white. The ceiling has a light fixture. 
The two areas are separated by a partial wall.
